create view business_rules.delivery_s_psa_c_componentdelivery
as

  select 
    bo."bk component",         -- business key for hub component
    bo."bk delivery",          -- business key for hub delivery
    bo."delivery guid",        -- delivery_guid from satellite delivery > psa > main
    bo."component name",       -- package_name from satellite component > psa > main
    bo."cbd number",           -- delivery_cbdnumber from satellite delivery > psa > main
    bo."component version",    -- component_version from satellite component > psa > main
    bo."component guid",       -- component_guid from satellite component > psa > main
    bo."delivery number",      -- delivery_deliverynumber from satellite delivery > psa > main
    bo."customer"              -- delivery_customer from satellite delivery > psa > main

  from businessobjects.delivery_s_psa_c_componentdelivery bo
